+---------------------------+-------+
| Variable_name | Value |
+---------------------------+-------+
| skip_parallel_replication | ON |
+---------------------------+-------+
 
SHOW VARIABLES LIKE \'innodb_sync_spin_loops\';
 
+------------------------+-------+
| Variable_name | Value |
+------------------------+-------+
| innodb_sync_spin_loops | 120 |
+------------------------+-------+
 
Using the inplace syntax:
 
