| Id | User | Host | db | Command | Time | State | Info |
Progress |
+-----+------+-----------+------+---------+------+-------+-----------------------+----------+
| 126 | root | localhost | NULL | Query | 0 | NULL | SHOW
FULL PROCESSLIST | 0.000 |
