variable has controlled interpretation of file names that
are given as literal strings.
 
Example
 
SELECT _utf8\'Hello world!\' INTO DUMPFILE \'/tmp/world\';
 
SELECT LOAD_FILE(\'/tmp/world\') AS world;
 
+--------------+
| world |
+--------------+
| Hello world! |
+--------------+
 


