| 1983-10-15 06:42:51 | Saturday | 7 | 5 |
| 2011-04-21 12:34:56 | Thursday | 5 | 3 |
| 2011-10-30 06:31:41 | Sunday | 1 | 6 |
| 2011-01-30 14:03:25 | Sunday | 1 | 6 |
| 2004-10-07 11:19:34 | Thursday | 5 | 3 |
+---------------------+------------+--------------+------------+
 

 
 
 
 
 
 
 

